Name: Macnamara
Description:
The Division of Macnamara consists of:

  • Port Phillip City Council,
  • part of Glen Eira City Council,
  • part of Melbourne City Council, and
  • part of Stonnington City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Manufacturing, commercial and retail enterprises and tourism.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of Dame Annie Jean Macnamara DBE, 1899-1968. Macnamara was a medical researcher and doctor who discovered there was more than one type of the polio virus and worked extensively with children suffering from poliomyelitis, training doctors and physiotherapists in the management of the disease.
Members: The first member for Macnamara will be elected at the next federal general election.
DemographicRating: Inner Metropolitan - situated in capital cities and consisting of well-established built-up suburbs.
